n%20impressively%20well-researched%20and%20up-to-date%20tracker%20of%20every%20sporting%20event%20Ted%20Cruz%20has%20attended%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Nanni%20finds%20little%20evidence%20of%20the%20Ted%20Cruz%20curse%20%E2%80%94%20with%20one%20important%20caveat%20that%20we'll%20get%20to.%20Of%20the%2034%20games%20Nanni%20confirmed%20Cruz%20attended%2C%20the%20teams%20Cruz%20supported%20won%2018%20times%20and%20lost%2016%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20sports%2C%20his%20record%20is%20remarkably%20uncursed.%20Of%20the%20six%20Houston%20Rockets%20games%20Cruz%20has%20attended%20in%20the%20NBA%2C%20they%20won%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20despite%20the%20Astros%20flaming%20out%20against%20the%20Rangers%2C%20of%20the%2017%20MLB%20games%20Cruz%20has%20attended%2C%20the%20Astros%20have%20won%2010.%20(Before%20the%202023%20post-season%20debacle%2C%20Cruz's%20MLB%20record%20was%20an%20impressive%2010-2).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENanni%20cleverly%20uses%20the%20Vegas%20point%20spread%2C%20which%20finds%20the%20team%20favored%20to%20win%2C%20and%20calculates%20that%20Cruz%20attending%20a%20game%20leads%20to%20slightly%20more%20expected%20wins%20than%20you'd%20expect%20in%20the%20NBA%20and%20MLB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20in%20baseball%20and%20basketball%20games%20where%20Cruz's%20team%20is%20the%20underdog%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20win%20more%20than%20you%20would%20expect%20when%20Cruz%20attends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20one%20black%20mark%20on%20Cruz's%20record%3A%20college%20football.%20There%2C%20Cruz%20truly%20does%20seem%20to%20bring%20some%20gnarly%20bad%20luck%20to%20bear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20eight%20games%20Cruz%20has%20attended%20in%20person%2C%20the%20team%20he%20is%20supporting%2C%20be%20it%20the%20Texas%20Longhorns%2C%20the%20Baylor%20Bears%2C%20or%20the%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM%20Aggies%2C%20loses%2085%25%20of%20the%20time%20for%20a%201-7%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20accounting%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20many%20of