on%20leaps%20for%20a%20catch%20during%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20the%202024%20Rose%20Bowl.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMark%20J.%20Terrill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMichigan%20quarterback%20J.J.%20McCarthy%20marched%20his%20offense%20onto%20the%20field%20with%204%3A41%20remaining%20and%20all%20of%20the%20pressure%20to%20score.%20McCarthy%20found%20star%20running%20back%20Blake%20Corum%20on%20fourth-and-2%20for%20a%2027-yard%20catch%20to%20break%20into%20Alabama%20territory%20and%20secure%20the%20first%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20junior%20QB%20broke%20away%20for%20a%2016-yard%20run%20on%20the%20very%20next%20play.%20Right%20after%20that%2C%20he%20found%20wide%20receiver%20Roman%20Wilson%2C%20who%20made%20a%20leaping%20catch%20for%20a%2029-yard%20gain%20that%20put%20the%20Wolverines%20in%20the%20red%20zone.%20Wilson%20hauled%20in%20a%20four-yard%20pass%20and%20crossed%20into%20the%20end%20zone%20a%20few%20plays%20later%20to%20tie%20the%20game%20up%20at%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Crimson%20Tide%20got%20the%20ball%20back%20with%2094%20seconds%20left%20in%20regulation%2C%20but%20several%20key%20stops%20from%20the%20Michigan%20defense%20forced%20Alabama%20to%20punt%20on%20what%20could%20have%20otherwise%20been%20a%20game-winning%20drive.%20The%20Wolverines%20narrowly%20avoided%20a%20safety%20on%20the%20other%20end%20and%20headed%20into%20overtime%20with%20momentum%20on%20their%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20only%20took%20two%20plays%20for%20Corum%20to%20find%20the%20end%20zone%20in%20overtime.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michigan%20running%20back%20Blake%20Corum%20broke%20several%20tackles%20en%20route%20to%20an%20OT%20touchdown.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65945d19ec62ab5daf800803%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichigan%20running%20back%20Blake%20Corum%20broke%20several%20tackles%20en%20route%20to%20an%20OT%20touchdown.%3Cp%3EKiyoshi%20Mio-USA%20TODAY%20Sports%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Crimson%20Tide%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20elected%20to%20start%20overtime%20on%20defense%2C%20but%20Michigan%20wasted%20no%20time%20making%20that%20decision%20look%20foolish.%20Corum%20ripped%20off%20an%20eight-yard%20run%20to%20start%20OT%2C%20then%20charged%20through%20Alabama's%20defense%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0breaking%20several%20tackles%20along%20the%20way%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20a%2017-yard%20touchdown%20run%20that%20gave%20the%20Wolverines%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20national%20championship%20on%20the%20line%2C%20Michigan's%20defense%20came%20up%20huge.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222223%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michigan%20DB%20Rod%20Moore%20tackles%20Alabama%20quarterback%20Jalen%20Milroe%20during%20overtime%20of%20the%202024%20Rose%20Bowl.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65945ec6ec62ab5daf80089e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichigan%20DB%20Rod%20Moore%20tackles%20Alabama%20quarterback%20Jalen%20Milroe%20during%20overtime%20of%20the%202024%20Rose%20Bowl.%3Cp%3EKirby%20Lee-USA%20TODAY%20Sports%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMilroe%20and%20the%20Crimson%20Tide%20offense%20had%20to%20find%20the%20end%20zone%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20their%20chances%20of%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20CFP%20National%20Championship%20game%20alive.%20But%20the%20Wolverine%20defense%2C%C2%A0which%20had%20put%20Milroe%20on%20his%20heels%20in%20the%20first%20half%2C%20stifled%20Alabama's%20attempts%20to%20break%20through%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Crimson%20Tide%20broke%20into%20the%20red%20zone%20after%20the%20quarterback%20found%20wide%20receiver%20Jermaine%20Burton%20for%20an%2011-yard%20completion.%20But%20on%20fourth-and-three%2C%20Michigan%20crushed%20Milroe's%20rush%20attempt%20well%20before%20the%20goal%20line%20to%20clinch%20the%20overti