l%20impacts%20of%20a%20collective%20trauma%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20survey's%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20factors%20like%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20global%20conflict%2C%20racism%2C%20racial%20injustice%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20climate-related%20disasters%20all%20contributed%20to%20Americans'%20anxiety%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20and%20emotional%20strain%20can%20feel%20inescapable%2C%20but%20I'm%20determined%20to%20leave%20it%20behind%20as%20we%20kick%20off%202024.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20ways%20I'm%20fighting%20stress%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIn%202024%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20kinder%20to%20myself%20by%20silencing%20my%20inner%20critic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Edmonds%20at%20the%20MOMA.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6594546a1c5c7b8c9a0d4ed9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20me%20at%20the%20Museum%20of%20Modern%20Art%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Fblog%2Fhuman-inner-dynamics%2F202312%2Funderstanding-the-inner-critic%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKey%2520points%2Csense%2520of%2520inadequacy%2520and%2520worthlessness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPsychology%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20when%20people%20are%20faced%20with%20hardships%2C%20some%20will%20experience%20mild%20self-criticism%20and%20may%20navigate%20the%20situation%20with%20self-compassion.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20people%20will%20have%20an%20%26quot%3Bunfriendly%26quot%3B%20inner%20voice%20that%20creates%20negative%20thoughts%20and%20distorts%20their%20perception%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20I've%20fallen%20into%20the%20nasty%20habit%20of%20listening%20to%20my%20inner%20critic's%20meanest%20jabs%2C%20