quoted%20her%20as%20questioning%20majoritarian%20interpretations%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20If%20a%20majority%20of%20people%20agree%2C%20can%20they%20always%20have%20a%20way%20over%20the%20remainder%3F%20What%20happens%20if%20the%20core%20interests%20of%20a%20small%20group%20are%20hurt%3F%20What%20is%20the%20remedy%20if%20a%20temporary%20majority%20insists%20on%20taking%20a%20decision%20which%20may%20have%20grave%20future%20consequences%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20an%20enduring%20but%20slim%20majority%20is%20formed%2C%20do%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20govern%20unchallenged%3F%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20people%20worry%20that%20their%20language%20or%20religious%20practice%20or%20way%20of%20life%20could%20be%20permanently%20threatened%20only%20because%20they%20were%20not%20many%20in%20number%2C%20it%20does%20not%20help%20peace%20or%20harmony%20in%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20also%20said%20that%20while%20people%20are%20familiar%20with%20concepts%20like%20secularism%20and%20democracy%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20meaning%20behind%20these%20concepts%20are%20often%20elusive%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20understanding%20of%20these%20terms%E2%80%9D%20will%20help%20Indians%20understand%20its%20past%20and%20prepare%20for%20future%20challenges%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20political%20scientists%20and%20commentators%20have%20said%20that%20India%20is%20experiencing%20democratic%20backsliding%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20V-Dem%20research%20institute%20categorised%20India%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.v-dem.net%2Fdocuments%2F12%2Fdr_2021.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Celectoral%20autocracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20deterioration%20in%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20media%2C%20academia%20and%20civil%20society.%3C%