20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20only%20after%20holding%20discussions%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fani%2Fstatus%2F1742215731025178901%5C%22%3EBhalla%20also%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20queues%20at%20petrol%20stations%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20have%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ecited%20industry%20officials%20as%20saying%20that%20around%202%2C000%20petrol%20stations%2C%20mostly%20located%20in%20northern%20and%20northwestern%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgovernment-begins-talks-as-truckers-protest-leads-to-panic-buying-of-fuel-2832908%5C%22%3Eran%20out%20of%20fuel%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20motorists%20were%20resorting%20to%20panic-buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20also%20cited%20station%20owners%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20saying%20that%20fuel%20stocks%20were%20set%20to%20run%20dry%20as%201%2C500%20tanker%20drivers%20who%20transport%20fuel%20to%20the%20Union%20territory%20were%20on%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20strikers%20in%20Rajasthan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fviolence-during-truckers-protest-in-rajasthans-kekri-three-police-personnel-injured%2Fcid%2F1991056%5C%22%3Eclashed%20with%20police%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20had%20gone%20to%20clear%20a%20traffic%20jam%20on%20Ajmer-Bhilwara%20highway%20when%20the%20mob%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20police%2C%20leaving%20three%20policemen%20injured.%20A%20vehicle%20of%20Kekri%20city%20%5Bin%20Rajasthan%5D%20police%20station%20was%20also%20burnt%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20an%20officer%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesting%20drivers%20from%20across%20the%20country%20have%20expressed%20alarm%20at%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20new%20criminal%20law%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20(BNS)%20passed%20by%20parliament%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20%E2%80%93%20that%20deals%20with%20hit-and-run%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20106(2)%20of%20the%20BNS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FBharatiya_Nyay_(Second)_Sanhita_2023.pdf%5C%22%3Eprescribes%20a%20ten-year%20prison%20term%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20fine%20to%20those%20who%20cause%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20of%20any%20person%20by%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving%20of%20vehicle%20not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide%20and%20escapes%20without%20reporting%20it%20to%20a%20police%20officer%20or%20a%20magistrate%20soon%20after%20the%20incident%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nationwide%20strike%20to%20protest%20this%20rule%20entered%20its%20second%20day%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrucker%20and%20transport%20organisations%20have%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20address%20this%20issue%20before%20protests%20escalate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftruckers-protest-10-year-jail-for-hit-and-run-cases%2Farticleshow%2F106459730.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Monday%2C%20protestors%20have%20blockaded%20roads%20and%20highways%20across%20states%2C%20including%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fnationwide-truckers-protest-maharashta-mp-gujarat-9091384%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20hundreds%20of%20truckers%20blocked%20National%20Highway%202%20near%20Dankuni%20toll%20plaza%20in%20Hooghly%20district%20for%20two%20hours%20on%20Sunday%2C%20burning%20tyres%20and%20parking%20their%20vehicles%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fwest-bengal-highway-chaos-in-dankuni-as-truckers-rally-against-stringent-hit-and-run-penalties%2Fcid%2F1990594%5C%22%3EPTI%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20appeal%20to%20drivers%20to%20maintain%20patience%20and%20uphold%20law%20and%20uphold%20law%20and%20order%20during%20this%20critical%20period.%20Our%20primary%20goal%20is%20to%20engage%20in%20constructive%20dialogue%20with%20the%20authorities%20to%20find%20a%20resolution%20that%20is%20fair%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bal%20Malkit%20Singh%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%20(AIMTC%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20truckers%E2%80%99%20body)%2C%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20upon%20the%20government%20to%20open%20channels%20for%20dialogue%20and%20work%20towards%20a%20solution%20that%20addresses%20concerns%20of%20all%20stakeholders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20quoted%20a%20senior%20official%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Transporters%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Association%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20home%20and%20transport%20ministries%20and%20other%20departments%20concerned.%20We%20understand%20that%20the%20law%20has%20several%20benefits%20but%20the%20few%20negative%20points%20will%20lead%20to%20immense%20harassment%2C%20extortion%2C%20unnecessary%20detention%20and%20legal%20consequences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704218140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F02105437%2Ftruck-390936_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftruckers-transporters-protest-10-year-sentence-for-hit-and-run-in-new-criminal-law%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meanwhile%2C%20some%20protesters%20in%20Rajasthan%20reportedly%20threw%20stones%20at%20police%20personnel%20and%20burned%20a%20police%20vehicle.%20Long%20queues%20have%20been%20reported%20at%20petrol%20stations%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftruckers-transporters-protest-10-year-sentence-for-hit-and-run-in-new-criminal-law%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20Deputy%20Head%20Killed%20In%20%26quot%3BTreacherous%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Strike%20In%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20war%20against%20Palestinian%20operatives%20reached%20into%20the%20Lebanese%20capital%20Beirut%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20where%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20killed%20Hamas's%20deputy%20leader%2C%20the%20group%20and%20security%20officials%20in%20Lebanon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high-level%20security%20official%20told%20AFP%20that%20Saleh%20al-Aruri%20was%20killed%20along%20with%20his%20bodyguards%20in%20the%20strike%20by%20Israel%2C%20which%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20after%20the%20movement's%20unprecedented%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20security%20official%20confirmed%20the%20information%2C%20adding%20two%20floors%20of%20the%20targeted%20building%20and%20one%20car%20were%20damaged.%20Lebanese%20state%20media%20reported%20the%20strike%20hit%20a%20Hamas%20office%20in%20Beirut's%20southern%20suburbs%2C%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Lebanon's%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20TV%20also%20said%20Israel%20had%20killed%20Aruri%20in%20Beirut.%20And%20Lebanese%20media%20said%20a%20total%20of%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20will%20add%20to%20persistent%20fears%20that%20the%20nearly%20three-month-old%20Israeli-Hamas%20war%20could%20become%20a%20wider%20conflagration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGunmen%20from%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20ruled%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20since%202007%2C%20killed%20around%201%2C140%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%20in%20their%20October%20attacks%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20operatives%20also%20took%20around%20250%20hostages%2C%20129%20of%20whom%20remain%20in%20captivity%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20worst%20attack%20in%20its%20history%2C%20Israel%20began%20a%20relentless%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20offensive%20that%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2022%2C185%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20battled%20Hamas%20operatives%20among%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20heavily-bombed%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20soldiers%20had%20killed%20%26quot%3Bdozens%20of%20terrorists%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20some%20carrying%20explosives%2C%20raided%20a%20weapons%20storage%20compound%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Khan%20Yunis%20and%20discovered%20long-range%20rocket%20launchers%20and%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas-run%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry%20said%2070%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20100%20wounded%20in%20the%20previous%2024%20hours%20during%20Israeli%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20Israel%20twice%20struck%20the%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20(PRCS)%20headquarters%2C%20PRCS%20said%2C%20resulting%20in%20%26quot%3Bfive%20casualties%20and%20three%20injuries%26quot%3B%20among%20displaced%20people%20who%20had%20sought%20refuge%20there%20and%20at%20a%20nearby%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20said%20four%20people%20were%20killed%20including%20an%20infant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20told%20us%20to%20go%20to%20the%20south%20that%20is%20safe%2C%20but%20they%20are%20liars%2C%26quot%3B%20shouted%20Fathi%20al-Af%2C%20pointing%20to%20his%20daughter%20on%20a%20stretcher%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20Nasser%20Hospital%20after%20the%20strike.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Gaza%20Strip%20is%20not%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20Nations%20agencies%20have%20voiced%20alarm%20over%20Gaza's%20spiralling%20humanitarian%20crisis%20that%20has%20left%202.4%20million%20people%20under%20siege%20and%20bombardment%2C%20most%20of%20them%20displaced%20and%20crowded%20into%20shelters%20and%20tents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20warned%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20famine%2C%20and%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccused%20mastermind%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20says%20173%20of%20its%20soldiers%20have%20been%20killed%20inside%20Gaza%20in%20the%20battle%20against%20Hamas%2C%20which%20is%20listed%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20news%20outlet%20Axios%2C%20citing%20unnamed%20Israeli%20sources%2C%20said%20Hamas%20had%20presented%20Israel%20with%20a%20proposal%20on%20Sunday%20for%20a%20new%20hostage%20exchange%20deal%20via%20Qatari%20and%20Egyptian%20mediators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20told%20Axios%20the%20proposal%20had%20been%20deemed%20unacceptable%20by%20the%20Israeli%20war%20cabinet%2C%20but%20suggested%20progress%20could%20be%20made%20towards%20a%20more%20amenable%20plan%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar-based%20Hamas%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20speaking%20on%20Tuesday%20before%20Aruri's%20death%2C%20said%20hostages%20will%20only%20be%20freed%20%26quot%3Bon%20terms%20set%20by%20the%20resistance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAruri%2C%20in%20early%20December%2C%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Zionist%20prisoners%20will%20be%20the%20release%20of%20all%20our%20prisoners%20--%20after%20a%20ceasefire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAruri%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20exile%2C%20is%20accused%20by%20Israel%20of%20masterminding%20numerous%20attacks.%20He%20was%20elected%20deputy%20to%20Haniyeh%20in%202017%2C%20before%20being%20officially%20named%20the%20group's%20number%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20the%20Israeli%20army%20demolished%20Aruri's%20home%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20televised%20address%20Tuesday%2C%20Haniyeh%20also%20said%20Hamas%20is%20%26quot%3Bopen%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20national%20government%20for%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20wrote%20in%20a%20newspaper%20opinion%20article%20that%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20should%20ultimately%20be%20%26quot%3Breunited%26quot%3B%20under%20a%20new%20Palestinian%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20its%20bloodiest%20ever%20Gaza%20war%2C%20Israel%20has%20had%20the%20backing%20of%20its%20ally%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20has%20however%20also%20urged%20greater%20restraint%20to%20spare%20civilian%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20government%2C%20which%20includes%20far-right%20and%20hardline%20nationalist%20groups%2C%20has%20said%20repeatedly%20it%20will%20keep%20fighting%20until%20Hamas%20is%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%202024%20started%2C%20a%20dispute%20that%20had%20split%20the%20nation%20for%20months%20prior%20to%20the%20war%20flared%20again.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20repeatedly%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20protest%20the%20judicial%20reforms%20proposed%20by%20the%20government%20of%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20is%20being%20tried%20on%20corruption%20charges%20he%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20overruled%20a%20key%20plank%20of%20the%20judicial%20overhaul%20that%20Netanyahu%20has%20defended%20as%20rebalancing%20the%20powers%20of%20politicians%20and%20judges%2C%20but%20which%20protesters%20--%20including%20military%2