-affects-both-the-films%2Farticleshow%2F106493512.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106493512.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEven%20before%20the%20release%20of%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20Dunki%20and%20Prabhas%20starrer%20Salaar%2C%20there%20was%20a%20growing%20tension%20between%20distributors%20and%20exhibitors%20regarding%20the%20advance%20bookings%20of%20both%20the%20films.%20However%2C%20the%20makers%20had%20maintained%20a%20stoic%20silence%20over%20the%20issue.%20While%20both%20Dunki%20and%20Salaar%20managed%20to%20rake%20in%20moolah%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20director%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%20recently%20admitted%20that%20the%20clash%20of%20films%20invariably%20affects%20box%20office%20returns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frajkumar-hirani-breaks-his-silence-on-dunki-vs-salaar-box-office-clash-it-affects-both-the-films%2Farticleshow%2F106493512.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Truckers%20End%20Stir%20After%20Centre%20Says%20'Hit-And-Run%20Law%20Decision%20After%20Talks'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20countrywide%20truckers'%20stir%20has%20been%20called%20off%20as%20the%20government%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20consult%20stakeholders%20before%20implementing%20a%20contentious%20law%20against%20hit-and-run.%20After%20long%20talks%20with%20the%20government%2C%20the%20All-India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%20called%20off%20the%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20discussion%20with%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%20representatives...%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20say%20that%20the%20new%20rule%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20yet.%20We%20all%20want%20to%20say%20that%20before%20implementing%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Samhita%20106%2F2%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20discussion%20with%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress%20representatives%20and%20then%20only%20we%20will%20take%20a%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Home%20Secretary%20Ajay%20Bhalla%20said%20this%20evening.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20new%20laws%20have%20not%20been%20implemented.%20It%20will%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20consultation%20with%20All%20India%20Transport%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20confirmed%20Bal%20Malkit%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20AIMTC's%20core%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20was%20over%20the%20Section%20106(2)%20of%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Samhita%20or%20BNS%20--%20which%20is%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20colonial-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20--%20which%20had%20provisions%20for%20strict%20penalty%20in%20hit-and-run%20cases.%20The%20truckers%20had%20threatened%20to%20hold%20an%20all-India%20strike%2C%20triggering%20panic%20about%20shortage%20of%20fuel%20and%20essential%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20had%20spread%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20including%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20law%2C%20hit-and-run%20cases%20can%20attract%20up%20to%2010%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh%20--%20against%20the%20current%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20two-year%20jail%20term%20and%20a%20lighter%20fine.%20The%20maximum%20punishment%20of%2010%20years%20will%20kick%20in%20where%20the%20offender%20has%20caused%20death%20through%20rash%20driving%20and%20decamped%20without%20reporting%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20police.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truckers%2C%20cab%20drivers%20and%20others%20operating%20commercial%20vehicles%20are%20questioning%20how%20they%20would%20pay%20such%20a%20steep%20fine%20in%20case%20they%20meet%20with%20an%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20warned%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20misuse%20of%20the%20law%2C%20the%20process%20of%20informing%20authorities%20given%20the%20risk%20of%20public%20anger%2C%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20evidence%20that%20will%20be%20acceptable%20in%20case%20of%20a%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704215820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhq2thv7g_truckers-protest-pti_625x300_01_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhit-and-run-stir-breakthrough-truckers-body-appeals-for-end-to-protests-4788602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20countrywide%20truckers'%20stir%20has%20been%20called%20off%20as%20the%20government%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20consult%20stakeholders%20before%20implementing%20a%20contentious%20law%20against%20hit-and-run.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhit-and-run-stir-breakthrough-truckers-body-appeals-for-end-to-protests-4788602%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhit-and-run-stir-breakthrough-truckers-body-appeals-for-end-to-protests-4788602%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhit-and-run-stir-breakthrough-truckers-body-appeals-for-end-to-protests-4788602%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Will%20Build%20Bridges%20With%20India'%3A%20Hindu%20Woman%20Who%20Will%20Contest%20Pak%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDr%20Saveera%20Parkash%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20candidate%20to%20contest%20the%20general%20elections%20from%20the%20Buner%20constituency%20in%20the%20restive%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province%2C%20has%20said%20that%2C%20if%20elected%2C%20she%20would%20help%20build%20diplomatic%20bridges%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20by%20profession%2C%2025-year-old%20Saveera%20filed%20her%20nomination%20papers%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20People's%20Party%20(PPP)