%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-build-bridges-with-india-hindu-who-filed-nomination-for-pakistan-polls-4788654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Saveera%20Parkash%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20candidate%20to%20contest%20the%20general%20elections%20from%20the%20Buner%20constituency%20in%20the%20restive%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province%2C%20has%20said%20that%2C%20if%20elected%2C%20she%20would%20help%20build%20diplomatic%20bridges%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-build-bridges-with-india-hindu-who-filed-nomination-for-pakistan-polls-4788654%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-build-bridges-with-india-hindu-who-filed-nomination-for-pakistan-polls-4788654%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwill-build-bridges-with-india-hindu-who-filed-nomination-for-pakistan-polls-4788654%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20MP's%20%26quot%3BCancer-Ridden%20Trinamool%26quot%3B%20Outburst%20Pricks%20INDIA%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20announcement%20that%20only%20her%20party%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20can%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20led%20to%20concerns%20over%20whether%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20will%20fructify%20in%20her%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20missed%20a%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20to%20start%20seat-sharing%20talks%20and%20its%20state%20president%20is%20now%20attacking%20the%20Trinamool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20who%20is%20opposed%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20tie-up%20with%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20has%20blasted%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20party%2C%20which%20he%20called%20is%20riddled%20with%20factionalism%2C%20for%20not%20following%20a%20uniform%2C%20c