20by%20the%20Sri%20Rama%20Vidya%20Kendra%20Trust%2C%20itself%20run%20by%20RSS%20functionary%20Kalladka%20Prabhakar%20Bhat%2C%20a%20rabid%20rabble%20rouser%20known%20for%20his%20communally%20charged%20statements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20school%20also%20came%20in%20the%20news%20in%20December%202019%2C%20when%20its%20students%20were%20made%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-school-run-rss-man-makes-kids-demolish-babri-masjid-play-114172%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ere-enact%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20school%20event%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20gave%20a%20speech%20eulogising%20Bhat%20and%20commending%20his%20efforts%20in%20providing%20value-based%20education%20to%20students%20and%20inculcating%20native%20culture%2C%20tradition%20and%20heritage%20in%20them.%20He%20also%20regretted%20his%20earlier%20statements%20critical%20of%20Bhat%20and%20ended%20his%20speech%20by%20saying%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FMangalore%2Fi-regret-criticising-rss-leader%2Farticle67624213.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20express%20my%20deep%20regret%20for%20criticism%20in%20the%20past%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20what%20some%20people%20had%20told%20me%20intending%20to%20mislead%20me.%20This%20visit%20today%20has%20transformed%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaster%20of%20U-turns%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Kumaraswamy%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20of%20mind%E2%80%9D.%20His%20mind%20seems%20to%20take%20a%20U-turn%20once%20every%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20when%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20Kumaraswamy