ms%20are%20starting%20flourish.%20If%20there%20was%20another%20window%2C%20I%20would%20have%20started%20a%20second%20T20%20league%20in%20a%20knockout%20where%20there%20would%20be%20teams%20competing%20and%20the%20top%20four%20sides%20would%20qualify%20for%20the%20second%20stage%20where%20the%20IPL%20teams%20may%20enter%20directly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20T10%20League%20which%20has%20been%20organised%20in%20the%20UAE%20since%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20details%20I%20am%20hearing%20from%20you%2C%20the%20T10%20league%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20tournament%20in%20which%20there%20will%20be%20a%20international%20club%20format.%20If%20I%20am%20right%2C%20it%20will%20be%20completely%20Doomsday%20from%20Day%201.%20Because%20there%20isn't%20a%20ICC%20T10%20tournament%2C%20all%20the%20members%20don't%20have%20a%20T10%20format%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704211800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F8g0q28jo_lalit-modi_625x300_17_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-may-start-t10-league-say-sources-but-lalit-modi-feels-itll-be-doomsday-4788319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20can%20a%20T10%20League%20impact%20Indian%20cricket%3F%20NDTV%20talked%20to%20former%20IPL%20commissioner%20Lalit%20Modi%20on%20the%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-may-start-t10-league-say-sources-but-lalit-modi-feels-itll-be-doomsday-4788319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-may-start-t10-league-say-sources-but-lalit-modi-feels-itll-be-doomsday-4788319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-may-start-t10-league-say-sources-but-lalit-modi-feels-itll-be-doomsday-4788319%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cabin%20crew%20of%20Japan%20Airlines