0company%20for%20nine%20years%20before%20Airtel%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fairtel-africa-announces-appointment-of-sunil-taldar-as-md-and-ceo-124010201037_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fairtel-africa-announces-appointment-of-sunil-taldar-as-md-and-ceo-124010201037_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fairtel-africa-announces-appointment-of-sunil-taldar-as-md-and-ceo-124010201037_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MGNREGA%3A%20After%20Pushback%20on%20Aadhaar-Based%20Pay%2C%20Govt%20Defensive%2C%20Says%20May%20Consider%20Exemptions%20Case-by-Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09120730%2FAadhaar-cards.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Facing%20backlash%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20may%20consider%20exemptions%20from%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20(ABPS)%20for%20the%20payment%20of%20wages%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccase%20to%20case%E2%80%9D%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20for%20the%20Act%2C%20which%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20work%20to%20rural%20households%2C%20was%20made%20mandatory%20on%20January%2030%2C%202023%20and%20kickstarted%20on%20Monday%20(January%201)%20after%20five%20extensions%20for%20state%20governments%20to%20calibrate%20their%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20requires%20a%20worker%E2%80%99s%20bank%20account%20and%20job%20card%20to%20be%20linked%20with%20Aadhaar.%20The%20account%20must%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98mapper%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnew-year-new-rule-for-mgnrega-workers%2Farticle67692863.ece%5C%22%3Edata%20provided%20by%20LibTech%20India%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20consortium%20of%20academics%20and%20activists%2C%207.6%20crore%20job%20cards%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%20over%20the%20last%2021%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1992238%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20late%20on%20Monday%20(January%201)%20night%2C%20the%20Union%20rural%20development%20ministry%20said%20that%20exemption%20from%20the%20ABPS%20can%20be%20considered%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccase%20to%20case%20basis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%2C%20if%20any%20gram%20panchayat%20of%20a%20district%20in%20the%20state%20is%20having%20either%20technical%20%5Bproblems%5D%20or%20Aadhaar-related%20%5Bproblems%5D%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20may%20consider%20exemption%20from%20APBS%20on%20%5Ba%5D%20case%20to%20case%20basis%20till%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20condemned%20the%20ABPS%20for%20the%20MGNREGA%20and%20called%20it%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcruel-new-year-gift-says-congress-as-mgnrega-wage-payment-through-aadhaar-system-kickstarts%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccruel%20new%20year%20gift%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20poor%20and%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20urged%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20weaponising%20technology%2C%20especially%20Aadhaar%2C%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20release%20delayed%20wage%20payments%20and%20implement%20open%20muster%20rolls%20and%20social%20audits%20to%20improve%20transparency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20ministry%20in%20its%20statement%20said%20that%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnoticed%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9Csome%20section%20of%20the%20newspapers%20has%20quoted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment%20should%20stop%20weaponizing%20technology%2C%20especially%20Aadhaar%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20release%20delay%20wage%20payment%20and%20implement%20open%20muster%20roll%20and%20social%20audits%20to%20improve%20transparency.%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20MGNREGA%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdemand-driven%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20use%20of%20technology%20has%20brought%20%E2%80%9Ca%20transformation%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMahatma%20Gandhi%20NREGA%20is%20a%20demand%20driven%20scheme%20and%20is%20affected%20by%20various%20economic%20factors.%20Total%20number%20of%20registered%20job%20cards%20is%2014.32%20crore%2C%20out%20of%20which%20just%209.77%20crore%20(68.22%25)%20is%20active%20job%20cards.%20There%20is%20a%20total%20of%2025.25%20crore%20workers%2C%20out%20of%20which%20just%2014.32%20crore%20(56.83%25)%20are%20active%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20use%20of%20different%20technologies%20ranging%20from%20space%20technology%2Fremote%20sensing%20to%20IT%20enabled%20technology%2C%20has%20brought%20a%20transformation%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20also%20refuted%20claims%20of%20any%20data%20being%20deleted%20due%20to%20the%20ABPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJob%20card%20of%20household%20can%20be%20deleted%20only%20in%20certain%20specific%20conditions%2C%20but%20not%20due%20to%20ABPS.%20Updation%2Fdeletion%20of%20job%20cards%20is%20a%20regular%20exercise%20conducted%20by%20the%20States%2FUTs.%20A%20job%20card%20can%20be%20deleted%20in%20case%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fake%20job%20card%20(incorrect%20job%20card)%2F%20duplicate%20job%20card%2F%20household%20not%20willing%20to%20work%2F%20family%20shifted%20from%20gram%20panchayat%20permanently%2F%20single%20person%20in%20job%20card%20and%20that%20person%20is%20expired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20April%202022%20to%20till%20date%2C%20about%202.85%20crore%20job%20cards%20have%20been%20deleted%20by%20following%20the%20due%20process%20by%20the%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20specific%20pilot%20study%20as%20well%20as%20consultation%20was%20done%20before%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20National%20Mobile%20Monitoring%20System%20(NMMS)%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20claim%20in%20the%20statement%20that%2034.8%25%20of%20total%20registered%20workers%20and%2012.7%25%20of%20active%20workers%20are%20still%20ineligible%20for%20ABPS%20has%20no%20relevance.%20Because%20APBS%20is%20applicable%20only%20in%20case%20a%20registered%20beneficiary%20turns%20ups%20for%20wage%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20wage%20payment%20of%20unskilled%20workers%20through%20APBS%20to%20ensure%20the%20payment%20of%20beneficiaries%20into%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20even%20in%20case%20of%20frequent%20change%20of%20bank%20account%20by%20the%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%2C%20if%20any%20gram%20panchayat%20of%20a%20district%20in%20the%20state%20is%20having%20either%20technical%20problem%20or%20Aadhaar-related%20problem%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20may%20consider%20exemption%20from%20APBS%20on%20case-to-case%20basis%20till%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704209505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09120730%2FAadhaar-cards.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Funion-government-may-consider-case-by-case-exemptions-to-abps-mgnregs%2