was%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team.%20We%20dominated%20in%20England%2C%20we%20fought%20hard%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20we%20won%20in%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20Srikkanth%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYxcH2_izYWw%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrikkanth%20also%20said%20that%20India%20need%20to%20forget%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20the%20No.%201%20ranked%20Test%20side%20in%20the%20world%20right%20now%20and%20even%20called%20some%20of%20the%20current%20players%20'overrated'.%20The%20former%20India%20opener%20also%20want%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kuldeep%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63624-kuldeep-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20more%20chances%20in%20order%20to%20utilise%20him%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20forget%20the%20ICC%20rankings.%20We%20are%20always%201-2%2C%201-2.%20It's%20a%20combination%20of%20having%20overrated%20cricketers%20and%20people%20who%20have%20not%20performed%20up%20to%20their%20potential.%20Or%20there%20are%20players%20who%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20chances%2C%20like%20Kuldeep%20(Yadav)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dean%20Elgar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1377-dean-elgar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDean%20Elgar%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20bid%20to%20bring%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20his%20Test%20career%20by%20skippering%20South%20Africa%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20second%20and%20final%20Test%20against%20an%20India%20side%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20make%20at%20least%20two%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tourists%20hopes%20of%20achieving%20their%20first%20ever%20series%20success%20in%20South%20Africa%20were%20comprehensively%20dashed%20as%20they%20lost%20the%20first%20Test%20by%20an%20innings-and-32%20runs%20last%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESou