ring%20a%20third%20was%20arrested%20in%20London%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%20days%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fcrime%2Fkimberlee-singler-murder-colorado-arrested-uk-b2472156.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20Kimberlee%20Singler%2C%2035%2C%20appeared%20at%20Westminister%20Magistrate's%20court%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20charged%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20her%20two%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingler%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20two%20counts%20of%20first-degree%20murder%2C%20one%20count%20of%20attempted%20murder%2C%20three%20counts%20of%20child%20abuse%20and%20one%20count%20of%20assault.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daughter%2C%20aged%20nine%2C%20and%20son%2C%20seven%20were%20found%20dead%20at%20a%20home%20in%20Colorado%20on%20December%2019%2C%20along%20with%20her%2011-year-old%20daughter%20who%20was%20injured%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-67857888%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Crime%20Agency%20(NCA)%20in%20the%20UK%20reported%20that%20she%20attended%20an%20extradition%20hearing%20at%20Westminster%20Magistrates'%20Court%20on%20Monday.%20Following%20the%20hearing%2C%20she%20was%20remanded%20in%20custody%2C%20with%20the%20next%20court%20appearance%20scheduled%20for%20January%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20NCA%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20Saturday%2030%20December%202023%20in%20the%20Kensington%20area%20of%20London%2C%20officers%20from%20the%20National%20Crime%20Agency's%20National%20Extradition%20Unit%20arrested%20a%2035-year-old%20female%20wanted%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20for%20offences%20including%20two%20counts%20of%20murder%20and%20one%20count%20of%20attempted%20murder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Colorado%20Springs%20Police%20Department%20issued%20a%20press%20release%20stating%20that%20they%20initially%20received%20a%20911%20call%20reporting%20a%20burglary%20at%20a%20residence%20in%20Colorado%20at%2000%3A29%20local%20time%20on%20December%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20arriving%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20Ms.%20Singler%20and%20her%20eldest%20daughter%20were%20discovered%20injured%20and%20received%20immediate%20treatment%20before%20being%20transported%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20according%20to%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20police%20force%20concluded%20that%20the%20initial%20report%20of%20a%20burglary%20was%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bunfounded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20release%2C%20it%20was%20confirmed%20that%20she%20was%20arrested%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20incident%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20said%20more%20information%20would%20be%20shared%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singler's%20ex-husband%20Kevin%20Wentz%20said%20he%20was%20devastated%20when%20he%20learned%20of%20his%20children's%20death%20and%20that%20he%20and%20his%20family%20%26quot%3Bare%20suffering%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20grief%20and%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704208500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjrdv5ifg_kimberlee-singler_625x300_02_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-accused-of-murdering-two-of-her-children-arrested-in-london-4788013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singler%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20two%20counts%20of%20first-degree%20murder%2C%20one%20count%20of%20attempted%20murder%2C%20three%20counts%20of%20child%20abuse%20and%20one%20count%20of%20assault.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-accused-of-murdering-two-of-her-children-arrested-in-london-4788013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-acc