C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2030%20T20%20specialists%2C%20including%20India%20and%20IPL%20stars%2C%20will%20be%20monitored%20ahead%20of%20the%20ICC%20event%20in%20Caribbean%20and%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20Agarkar%20and%20his%20colleagues%20select%20both%20Rohit%20and%20Kohli%20for%20the%20short%20series%20starting%20January%2011%20in%20Mohali%20or%20directly%20check%20their%20form%20and%20fitness%20during%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20contemporary%20legends%20have%20apparently%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20would%20very%20much%20like%20to%20be%20part%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20England%20Tests%20starting%20in%20Hyderabad%20from%20January%2025%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20even%20if%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20are%20selected%2C%20they%20would%20play%20beyond%20a%20couple%20of%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20fit.%20The%20Afghanistan%20series%20won't%20tell%20you%20anything.%20Everything%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20first%20month%20of%20IPL%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkload%20management%20and%20monitoring%20core%20group%20during%20IPL%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20brass%20knows%20that%20they%20can't%20tell%20any%20franchise%20to%20optimally%20use%20a%20potential%20pick%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20June-July%20after%20IPL%20concludes%20in%20last%20week%20of%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BCCI%20can%20never%20tell%20a%20franchise%20to%20manage%20a%20star%20player's%20workload%20unless%20it's%20a%20case%20of%20injury%20management%2C%E2%80%9D%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20at%20least%2025%20to%2030%20players%20are%20zeroed%20in%20and%20monitored%20closely%20during%20the%20two%20months%20of%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20be%20a%20case%20of%20injury%20or%20fitness%20issue%20during%20the%20IPL%20and%20the%20selection%20committee%20would%20need%20two%20players%20for%20each%20slot%2C%20so%20that%20the%20like-for-like%20replacement%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20player%20whose%20ready%20replacement%20won't%20be%20available%20is%20Mumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704201780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbs6kptd_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-reuters-_625x300_25_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-rohit-sharma-keen-on-t20-world-cup-crucial-bcci-meeting-to-take-place-report-4787385%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20expected%20that%20Agarkar%20and%20Co%20will%20speak%20to%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20along%20with%20Test%20and%20ODI%20skipper%20Rohit%2C%20star%20batter%20Kohli%20before%20announcing%20the%20squad%20against%20Afghanistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-rohit-sharma-keen-on-t20-world-cup-crucial-bcci-meeting-to-take-place-report-4787385%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-rohit-sharma-keen-on-t20-world-cup-crucial-bcci-meeting-to-take-place-report-4787385%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-rohit-sharma-keen-on-t20-world-cup-crucial-bcci-meeting-to-take-place-report-4787385%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ananya%20celebrated%20New%20Year%20with%20Aditya%20in%20London%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704201723000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106490479%2Cimgsize-54674.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-celebrated-new-year-in-london-with-beau-aditya-roy-kapur-see-leaked-photo%2Farticleshow%2F106490479.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106490479.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAnanya%20Panday%20and%20Aditya%20Roy%20Kapur%2C%20rumored%20to%20be%20dating%2C%20celebrated%20their%20New%20Year%20together%20on%20a%20London%20vacation.%20A%20photo%20of%20the%20couple%20surrounded%20by%20friends%20shows%20them%20embracing%20each%20other%20closely.%20Ananya%20looks%20gorgeous%20in%20a%20plaid%20skirt%20suit%20paired%20with%20thigh-high%20boots%2C%20while%20Aditya%20complements%20her%20in%20a%20black%20blazer%20and%20turtle%20neck%20pullover.%20The%20photo%20received%20likes%20and%20comments%20from%20fans%20praising%20Ananya's%20outfit%20and%20their%20chemistry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-celebrated-new-year-in-london-with-beau-aditya-roy-kapur-see-leaked-photo%2Farticleshow%2F106490479.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20Teen%20Bites%20Mouse%20On%20Its%20Head%20After%20It%20Attacked%20Her%20Finger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bizarre%20case%2C%20a%20teen%20in%20China%20who%20was%20bitten%20by%20a%20mouse%20took%20revenge%20on%20the%20rodent%20by%20biting%20it%20back.%20The%20incident%20that%20has%20stunned%20social%20media%20users%C2%A0took%20place%20on%20December%2021%2C%202023%2C%20after%20the%2018-year-old%20woman%20was%20bitten%20on%20her%20finger%20by%20a%20mouse%20at%20her%20university%20dormitory%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Fenvironment%2Farticle%2F3246246%2Fbiggest-daredevil-2023-china-student-takes-revenge-mouse-bit-her-sinking-teeth-rodents-head-shocking%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Enraged%2C%20she%C2%A0decided%20to%20take%C2%A0matters%20into%20her%20own%20hands.%20Instead%20of%20using%20a%20mouse%20trap%2C%20or%20shooing%20the%20mouse%20away%2C%20the%20teen%20decided%20to%20catch%20it%20herself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20caught%20the%20pesky%20rodent%2C%20held%20it%20in%20her%20hands%2C%20and%20proceeded%20to%20bite%20it%20on%20its%20head%20in%20vengeance%2C%20leaving%20two%20teeth%20marks.%20The%20mouse%20died%20soon%20after%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20the%20firm%20gripping%20by%20the%20girl%20which%20led%20to%20suffocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20she%20also%20suffered%20injuries%20to%20her%20lips%20as%20a%20result%20of%20sinking%20her%20teeth%20into%20the%20rodent.%C2%A0The%20student%20later%20said%20on%20her%20own%20Douyin%20account%20that%20she%20had%20received%20prompt%20treatment%20and%20was%20fine.%C2%A0Her%20roommate%20additionally%20stated%20that%20she%20instantly%20regretted%20her%20conduct%20and%20was%20ashamed%20of%20exposing%20her%20face%20throughout%20the%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20doctor%20who%20attended%20the%20woman%20said%20he%20had%20never%20seen%20this%20before.%20''It%20took%20the%20doctor%20a%20while%20to%20work%20out%20how%20to%20write%20up%20her%20case%20file%2C''%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20bizarre%20actions%20startled%20and%20amused%20mainland%20social%20media%20users.%C2%A0The%20incident%20elicited%20a%20wave%20of%20jokes%2C%20with%20some%20users%20inviting%20her%20to%20assist%20with%20their%20mouse%20problems%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20hereby%20announce%20her%20as%20the%20biggest%20daredevil%20of%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20user%20wrote.%20''Do%20you%20want%20to%20watch%20over%20our%20rice%20barns%3F''%20another%20user%20commented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20student's%20roommate%20cautioned%20against%20imitating%20such%20actions%2C%20highlighting%20the%20risk%20of%20contracting%20a%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%C2%A0Rats%20and%20mice%20are%20known%20to%20carry%20many%20diseases.%20These%20diseases%20can%20spread%20to%20people%20directly%2C%20through%20the%20handling%20of%20rodents%2C%20contact%20with%20rodent%20feces%20(poop)%2C%20urine%2C%20or%20saliva%2C%20or%20rodent%20bites.%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20a%20rodent%20infestation%20and%20contact%20with%20rodents%20is%20to%20remove%20food%20sources%2C%20water%2C%20and%20items%20that%20provide%20shelter%20for%20rodents.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704201720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fgmjsoam_mouse_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fchinese-teen-catches-and-bites-mouse-on-its-head-after-it-attacked-her-finger-4787325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20caught%20the%20pesky%20rodent%2C%20held%20it%20tightly%20in%20her%20hands%2C%20and%20proceeded%20to%20bite%20it%20on%20its%20head%20in%20vengeance%2C%20leaving%20two%20teeth%20marks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fchinese-teen-catches-and-bites-mouse-on-its-head-after-it-attacked-her-finger-4787325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fchinese-teen-catches-and-bites-mouse-on-its-head-after-it-attacked-her-finger-4787325%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fchinese-teen-catches-and-bites-mouse-on-its-head-after-it-attacked-her-finger-4787325%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20With%20%26quot%3BAdvisers%26quot%3B%20Like%20These%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Needs%20No%20Enemies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20trusted%20advisors%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20making%20statements%20that%20queer%20the%20pitch%20for%20the%20Congress%20before%20elections.%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20comment%20on%20Ayodhya%3B%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EJo%20hua%20toh%20hua%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(what%20happened%20just%20happened)%20aside%20on%20the%201984%20Sikh%20riots%20before%20the%202019%20polls%3B%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar's%20'chaiwala'%20jibe%20on%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202014%20and%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eneech%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20comment%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%202019%20have%20all%20been%20disowned%20by%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20over%20the%20years.%20But%2C%20they%20caused%20indelible%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20leadership%20often%20relies%20on%20the%20expertise%20of%20professionals.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20in%20recent%20decades%2C%20apolitical%20professional%20advisers%20have%20emerged%20as%20factotum.%20The%20idea%20of%20a%20National%20Advisory%20Council%20(NAC)%2C%20comprising%20civil%20society%20and%20NGO%20activists%20and%20headed%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20credited%20to%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%C2%A0The%20NAC%20became%20the%20super-government%20in%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20era%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20governance%20earned%20the%20eminent%20economist%2C%20the%20harbinger%20of%20the%201991%20reforms%2C%20the%20charge%20of%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20paralyses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManmohan%20Singh's%20pioneering%20role%20in%20opening%20up%20the%20economy%20in%201991%20notwithstanding%2C%20the%20green%20activist%20stance%20of%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20as%20Environment%20Minister%20alienated%20the%20industry.%20He%20was%20shifted%20by%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister.%20His%20comments%20muddied%20the%20waters%20for%20his%20successor%20in%20the%20Environment%20Ministry%2C%20Jayanthi%20Natarajan.%20She%20faced%20graft%20charges%2C%20which%20she%20was%20absolved%20of%20by%20courts.%20The%20damage%20to%20the%20Congress%20image%20endured%2C%20impacting%20its%202014%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Pitroda%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20or%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20former%20bureaucrat%20K%20Raju%2C%20whom%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20relies%20upon%20over%20active%20politicians%2C%20are%20professionals%20par%20excellence%20but%20none%20of%20them%20have%20emerged%20from%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20Congress%20organisation.%20They%20perhaps%20are%20alien%20to%20the%20idiom%20of%20Indian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20professionals%20as%20ministers%20but%20they%20do%20not%20dominate%20the%20party's%20discourse.%20That%20role%20is%20assigned%20to%20those%20who%20have%20risen%20through%20the%20organisation%2C%20in%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20or%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20Decision-making%20in%20the%20BJP%20is%20strictly%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20its%20political%20nucleus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20in%20awe%20of%20is%20psephologist%20Yogendra%20Yadav.%20A%20core%20member%20of%20Anna%20Hazare's%20anti-corruption%20movement%20aimed%20at%20the%20Congress%20regime%2C%20Yadav%20failed%20to%20impress%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20thus%2C%20did%20not%20find%20place%20in%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP).%20Having%20walked%20with%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20he%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20Rahul%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Congress's%20reverses%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%2C%20Yadav%20has%20comforted%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20by%20calculating%20that%20Congress%20polled%2010%20lakh%20votes%20more%20than%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20November%20elections.%20Sources%20say%20he%20has%20told%20Rahul%20that%20the%20Congress%20can%20win%2028%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20according%20to%20his%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Yadav's%20'calculus'%2C%20a%20seasoned%20Congress%20leader%20shared%20a%20story%20about%20a%20mathematician%20who%20had%20to%20cross%20a%20river%20with%20his%20family.%20He%20calculated%20the%20mean%20flow%20of%20water%20in%20the%20river.%20He%20calculated%20his%20family's%20collective%20average%20height.%20Along%20with%20his%20son%2C%20daughter%20and%20wife%20he%20started%20crossing%20the%20river.%20The%20flow%20in%20the%20middle%20was%20strong%20and%20the%20water%20was%20deep.%20One%20by%20one%2C%20his%20family%20members%20were%20swept%20away.%20The%20mathematician%20somehow%20reached%20the%20opposite%20bank.%20He%20revisited%20his%20calculation%2C%20pulling%20his%20hair%20in%20despair%20he%20shouted%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ENadi%20ka%20paani%20jyon%20ka%20tyon%2C%20par%20kunba%20dooba%20kyon%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(The%20river%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20then%20why%20did%20the%20family%20drown%3F).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor%20was%20credited%20by%20many%20as%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20BJP's%202014%20strategy.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20after%20the%20elections%20he%20met%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMai%20ke%20baad%20kya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(what%20after%20May)%3F%26quot%3B%20Shah%20apparently%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BJune%26quot%3B.%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20who%20eventually%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20continues%20to%20advise%20a%20potpourri%20of%20parties.%20At%20one%20stage%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20appointed%20him%20as%20his%20second%20in%20command%20in%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU).%20He%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20is%20now%20on%20a%20padyatra%20in%20Bihar.%20His%20protege%2C%20Sunil%20Kanugolu%2C%20advised%20the%20Congress%20during%20the%20Karnataka%20election.%20After%20the%20Congress%20won%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20cabinet-rank%20adviser%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government.%20He%20was%20the%20Congress's%20strategist%20for%20the%20November%20state%20elections.%20Barring%20Telangana%2C%20his%20strategising%20did%20not%20work%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20in%20the%20Congress%20is%20divided%20on%20the%20feasibility%20of%20the%20'hybrid'%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20beginning%20on%20January%2014.%20Sources%20in%20the%20party%20say%20that%20doubts%20about%20the%20timing%20and%20cost%20of%20the%2065-day%20march%20across%2014%20states.%20The%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20meeting%20on%20December%2021%20saw%20even%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20expressing%20mild%20reservation%20as%20some%20members%20questioned%20its%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20turned%20to%20crowd-funding%20to%20refurbish%20its%20resources.%20QR%20codes%20were%20placed%20behind%20chairs%20at%20the%20party's%20139th%20anniversary%20celebration%20at%20Nagpur.%20Participants%20were%20encouraged%20to%20donate%20money%20by%20clicking%20on%20the%20QR%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20is%20said%20to%20have%20suggested%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20that%20he%20is%20the%20party's%20'face'%20for%20the%20general%20election%20campaign%20and%20so%2C%20may%20like%20to%20devote%20his%20energy%20to%20key%20constituencies.%20To%20this%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20reaction%20was%20that%20his%20job%20was%20to%20create%20the%20'%3Cem%3Emahaul%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(environment)%20and%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20the%20campaign%20was%20Kharge's%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20meeting%2C%20apart%20from%20pot%20shots%20at%20Kamal%20Nath%20for%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20loss%2C%20an%20interaction%20between%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20some%20members%20who%20alleged%20that%20his%20'corrupt%20image'%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20defeat%20is%20in%20circulation.%20Chagrined%2C%20Baghel%20is%20said%20to%20have%20retorted%20that%20funds%20are%20not%20raised%20through%20selling%20wild%20berries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20campaign%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20described%20the%20Baghel%20regime%20as%20the%20ATM%20(any-time%20money)%20machine%20of%20Congress.%20The%20perception%20was%20that%20Baghel%20managed%20the%20funds%20for%20the%20Congress's%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20campaign%20in%202022%20and%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20polls.%20Also%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20capital%20Raipur%20hosted%20the%20Congress%20plenary%20endorsing%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20beginning%20his%20Nyay%20Yatra%20on%20January%2014%2C%20Rahul%20will%20sidestep%20the%20January%2022%20mega%20event%20in%20Ayodhya.%20His%20choice%20of%20Imphal%20in%20Manipur%20-%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20talked%20about%20Pasighat%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20as%20the%20starting%20point%20when%20he%20announced%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%202.0%20in%20March%20last%20-%20is%20understandable%2C%20given%20his%20avowed%20concern%20for%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJairam%20Ramesh%20had%20called%20it%20a%20Pasighat%20to%20Porbandar%20yatra.%20Now%20it%20is%20Imphal-Mumbai.%20The%20decision%20to%20bypass%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20altogether%20has%20prompted%20leaders%20like%20Mahesh%20Jethmalani%20-%20a%20nominated%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20-%20to%20question%20if%20the%20%26quot%3Baversion%20to%20Arunachal%26quot%3B%20stems%20from%20the%20recent%20stance%20of%20China%2C%20which%20has%20renamed%2011%20places%20in%20the%20border%20state%20it%20lays%20claim%20to.%20Jethmalani%2C%20citing%20the%20agreement%20signed%20between%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20in%202007%2C%20has%20raised%20uncomfortable%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20launches%20his%20second%20yatra%20this%20month%2C%20the%20subject%20may%20generate%20political%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704200700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fr87rmhng_rahul-gandhi-yatra_625x300_27_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwith-advisers-like-these-rahul-gandhi-needs-no-enemies-4787265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi's%20trusted%20advisors%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20making%20statements%20that%20queer%20the%20pitch%20for%20the%20Congress%20before%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwith-advisers-like-these-rahul-gandhi-needs-no-enemies-4787265%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwith-advisers-like-these-rahul-gandhi-needs-no-enemies-4787265%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwith-advisers-like-these-rahul-gandhi-needs-no-enemies-4787265%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hasdeo%20Arand%20Deforestation%20Raises%20Questions%20of%20Adivasi%20Justice%20for%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20First%20Tribal%20CM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10192940%2FGA6N65IaQAAU8Yf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20tree%20felling%20for%20Parsa%20East%20and%20Kanta%20Basan%20(PEKB)%20phase-2%20extension%20coal%20mines%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20forest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fchhattisgarh%2Famid-protests-tree-felling-for-mine-extension-in-biodiversity-rich-hasdeo-arand-in-chhattisgarh-begins-2821733%5C%22%3Ehas%20begun%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20protests%20from%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20and%20activists.%20The%20question%20whether%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%20will%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter%20has%20immediately%20become%20a%20dominant%20concern%2C%20and%20perhaps%2C%20the%20first%20big%20challenge%20for%20the%20newly%20appointed%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20activists%20fighting%20for%20Adivasi%20rights%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20having%20a%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20if%20he%20continues%20to%20overlook%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20priorities%20to%20facilitate%20corporate%20interests%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20known%20for%20its%20rich%20mineral%20wealth%20underneath%20dense%20forests%20that%20has%20been%20home%20to%20Adivasis%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20got%20its%20first%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20felt%20that%20maybe%20he%20will%20act%20in%20their%20interests.%20But%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20Adivasis%20are%20being%20oppressed%20and%20corporate%20interests%20are%20being%20upheld%20in%20Hasdeo%2C%20it%20has%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20is%20%5Bwearing%5D%20a%20mere%20mask%2C%20and%20what%20corporates%20will%20decide%2C%20only%20that%20will%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alok%20Shukla%2C%20convenor%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2022%2C%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20in%20the%20biodiversity%20rich%20forest%20started%20despite%20protests%20from%20locals%20and%20activists.%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20is%20one%20of%20the%20last%20unfragmented%20forest%20landscapes%20in%20central%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20across%20over%201%2C500%20kilometres%20through%20central%20India%2C%20the%20area%20is%20home%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20communities%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20five%20billion%20tonnes%20of%20coal%20buried%20under%20the%20dense%20forests.%20Mining%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20business%20in%20the%20area%2C%20leading%20to%20protests%20by%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20what%20%E2%80%9Ctransitioning%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%E2%80%9D%20looks%20like%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20BJP%20government%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20resumed%20the%20task%20of%20clearing%20the%20Hasdeo%20forest%20for%20coal%20mines!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20communities%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20fight%20to%20save%20the%20forest.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmsMT9u2KrC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmsMT9u2KrC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Avinash%20Chanchal%20(%40avinashchanchl)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Favinashchanchl%2Fstatus%2F1738054081015664657%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fadani-mine-chhattisgarh-expansion-scroll%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20by%20%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20been%20excavating%20coal%20from%20the%20PEKB%20mine%20since%202013%20on%20behalf%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20state%20electricity%20generation%20company%2C%20Rajasthan%20Rajya%20Vidyut%20Utpadan%20Nigam%20Limited%2C%20to%20whom%20it%20was%20originally%20allocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20alleged%20that%20those%20who%20were%20travelling%20to%20the%20area%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20December%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20Adivasi%20activists%2C%20including%20Ramlal%20Kariam%2C%20Jayandan%20Porte%2C%20and%20Thakur%20Ram%2C%20were%20picked%20up%20from%20their%20homes%20and%20detained.%20Shukla%20himself%20was%20stopped%20by%20some%20persons%20who%20were%20not%20in%20police%20uniform%2C%20while%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Hasdeo%20on%20December%2022%20morning.%20They%20were%20taken%20to%20Bilaspur%20and%20released%20late%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20left%20from%20Raipur%20and%20was%20on%20my%20way%20to%20Hasdeo%20to%20meet%20other%20activists%2C%20and%20I%20was%20picked%20up%20on%20the%20way%20and%20taken%20to%20Bilaspur.%20Ajay%20T.G.%2C%20who%20is%20a%20documentary%20filmmaker%2C%20was%20also%20with%20me.%20After%20Ajay%20contacted%20some%20lawyers%20around%204%20pm%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20word%20of%20our%20detention%20got%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20new%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20has%20denied%20that%20the%20police%20detained%20anyone%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Sai%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20blamed%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20see%20that%20the%20permission%20for%20deforestation%20is%20from%20a%20time%20when%20it%20was%20their%20(Congress)%20government%20in%20power%E2%80%A6%20Whatever%20has%20happened%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20deforestation%2C%20is%20happening%20with%20their%20permission%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20as%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fchhattisgarh-cm-sai-singh-deo-join-the-debate-over-deforestation-in-hasdeo%2Farticle67674776.ece%5C%22%3E%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20Ambikapur%20MLA%20T.S.%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20a%20political%20strongman%20from%20the%20Sarguja%20region%20where%20Hasdeo%20is%20located%2C%