Hasdeo%20Arand%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20hundreds%20of%20villagers%20from%20the%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20area%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fhasdeo-aranya-mining-clearance-centre-trampling-on-tribal-rights-say-activists%5C%22%3Ehad%20walked%20300%20kms%20to%20Raipur%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20protest%20against%20mining%20in%20the%20area.%20They%20had%20met%20then%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20governor%20Anasuya%20Uikey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20October%2023%2C%202021%2C%20the%20governor%20wrote%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20probe%20these%20fake%20consents%2C%20however%2C%20no%20enquiry%20has%20been%20done.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20nothing%20has%20been%20done%20to%20give%20justice%20to%20the%20Adivasis%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20July%2026%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20passed%20a%20unanimous%20resolution%20that%20mining%20activities%20will%20not%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20Hasdeo.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20deforestation%20activities%20have%20now%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-new-mining-reserves-required-in-hasdeo-chhattisgarh-tells-sc-101689706977387.html%5C%22%3Eaffidavit%20%3C%2Fa%3E%20submitted%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20in%20July%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20wherein%20it%20was%20stated%20that%2C%20aside%20from%20the%20PEKB%20project%2C%20there%20is%20no%20necessity%20to%20allocate%20or%20use%20any%20new%20mining%20reserve%20areas%20for%20mining%20in%20Hasdeo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20a%20resolution%20passed%20unanimously%20by%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20or%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20affidavit%2C%20or%20overlooking%20the%20gram%20sabhas%E2%80%99%20opposition%2C%20all%20efforts%20have%20become%20null%20and%20void%20in%20the%20face%20of%20corporate%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Raipur-based%20political%20commentator%2C%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%2C%20said%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20taking%20away%20the%20Adivasi%20community%E2%80%99s%20rights%20over%20land%20for%20corporate%20interests%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20taking%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20work%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%20had%20taken%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20(Raman%20Singh%20government%2C%20from%202013%20to%202018)%20work%20forward%20and%20now%20the%20BJP%20is%20taking%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20work%20forward.%20In%20the%20area%20where%20deforestation%20is%20taking%20place%20now%2C%20under%20the%20Congress%20regime%2C%2043%20hectares%20of%20trees%20were%20cut%20last%20year%20(2022).%20In%20the%20same%20area%2C%2091%20acres%20were%20cut%20this%20year%20(2023).%20Now%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20here.%20There%20is%20nothing%20new%20with%20the%20new%20government%20or%20with%20a%20new%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20or%20a%20previous%20non-tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20several%20villages%20that%20are%20not%20part%20of%20Hasdeo%20but%20are%20part%20of%20Raipur%2C%20Bilaspur%2C%20Kanker%2C%20Durg%20zilas%2C%20villagers%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20out%20protest%20marches%20apart%20from%20the%20organisations%20working%20to%20protect%20Hasdeo.%20These%20protests%20will%20likely%20intensify%20as%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20continue%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20to%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fin-chhattishgarh-adanis-coal-mine-leaves-a-village-parched-this-monsoon%5C%22%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20Coal%20Mine%20Leaves%20a%20Village%20Parched%20This%20Monsoon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdivasi%20anger%20fuelled%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20victory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20November%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-chhattisgarh-congresss-cautious-pessimism-proves-to-be-too-little-too-late%5C%22%3Eunseated%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Congress%20government%20by%20winning%2054%20of%20the%2090%20assembly%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20only%20managed%20to%20win%20only%2035%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20approximately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribal.nic.in%2FST%2FTribal%2520Profile.pdf%5C%22%3E30%25%20of%20the%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20tribals%2C%20the%20state%20witnessed%20the%20appointment%20of%20its%20first%20tribal%20chief%20minister%2C%20Sai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20won%2025%20of%20the%2029%20reserved%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20polls%2C%20secured%20only%2011%20this%20time.%20The%20BJP%20improved%20its%20tally%20from%20three%20in%202018%20to%2017%20seats%20dominated%20by%20tribals%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20tribal%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Arvind%20Netam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhattisgarh-adivasis-bjp-congress-arvind-netam%5C%22%3Ewho%20quit%20the%20Congress%20last%20year%20to%20float%20his%20own%20political%20outfit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Hamar%20Raj%20Party%2C%20said%20that%20the%20reason%20behind%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20these%20elections%20was%20its%20neglect%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20dilution%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20(PESA)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PESA%20law%2C%20passed%20in%201996%2C%20seeks%20to%20provide%20a%20sense%20of%20autonomy%20to%20the%20local%20Adivasis%20by%20making%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20gram%20sabhas%20in%20Adivasi%20areas%20mandatory%20for%20projects%20in%20the%20region.%20When%20the%20Congress%20government%20notified%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fchhattisgarh-govt-implements-pesa-rule-2022%2Farticle65751589.ece%5C%22%3Eimplemented%20the%20PESA%20rules%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20(almost%2025%20years%20after%20the%20law%20was%20passed)%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cconsent%E2%80%9D%20of%20gram%20sabhas%20was%20changed%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fcongress-chhattisgarh-pesa-rules-activist-fire-8087658%2F%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cconsultation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20behind%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20is%20that%20the%20previous%20Congress%20government%20neglected%20the%20tribal%20community.%20Under%20the%20PESA%20law%2C%20the%20tribal%20community%20was%20granted%20rights%20and%20control%20over%20jal%20(water)%2C%20jungle%20(forest)%2C%20and%20zameen%20(land)%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20government%20diluted%20these%20provisions.%20This%20was%20the%20primary%20issue%20that%20led%20to%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20Bastar%2C%20at%20least%2020-22%20places%20have%20ongoing%20andolan%20(agitation)%20for%20over%20a%20year%20on%20jal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen.%20Either%20completely%20abolish%20PESA%2C%20or%20as%20long%20as%20the%20law%20exists%2C%20people%20will%20continue%20to%20speak%20up%2C%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20Netam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F23175928%2FWhatsApp-Image-2021-10-23-at-5.54.23-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F2317592