%20villages%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity%2C%20continued%20to%20struggle%20to%20bury%20their%20dead%20and%20faced%20social%20boycott.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Narayanpur%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20following%20soft%20Hindutva%20and%20did%20not%20act%20to%20protect%20those%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20Riots%20were%20reported%2C%20apart%20from%20attacks%20on%20church%2C%20and%20not%20allowing%20burials%20of%20those%20who%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%20While%20the%20Hindutva%20supporters%20in%20the%20region%20were%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20anyway%2C%20the%20Adivasi%20Christians%20were%20also%20disappointed%20because%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20to%20protect%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bastar-based%20lawyer%20and%20activist%20Bela%20Bhatia%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20policies%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20haven%E2%80%99t%20acted%20differently%20for%20the%20tribal%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Adivasi%20community%20expected%20an%20adequate%20shift%20when%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power.%20It%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fchhattisgarh-christians-hindutva-communalism%5C%22%3Enot%20that%20attacks%20on%20Christians%20were%20new%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20increased%20during%20the%20Congress%20years%2C%20and%20the%20government%20did%20not%20handle%20it%20boldly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20said%20that%20Adivasi%20anger%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20also%20intensified%20due%20to%20its%20inaction%20on%20judicial%20inquiry%20reports%20regarding%20fake%20encounters%20that%20occurred%20under%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government.%20These%20reports%20surfaced%20during%20the%20Baghel%20years%20but%20were%20not%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202012%2C%2017%20villagers%20were%20gunned%20down%20in%20an%20alleged%20encounter%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20alleged%20Maoists%20in%20Barstar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbastar-fake-encounter-maoists-inquiry%5C%22%3ESarkeguda.%3C%2Fa%3E%20A%20judicial%20inquiry%20report%20by%20retired%20Justice%20V.K.%20Agarwal%20in%202019%20found%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20those%20who%20were%20killed%20or%20injured%20by%20security%20forces%20were%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20inquiry%20report%20by%20Justice%20Agarwal%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjudicial-enquiry-finds-victims-of-chhattisgarh-were-not-maoists%5C%22%3EEdesmetta%20encounter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20eight%20tribals%20were%20killed%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20May%2017%20and%2018%2C%202013%2C%20when%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20opened%20fire%20on%20villagers%20who%20had%20gathered%20to%20celebrate%20%3Cem%3Ebeej%20pandum%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Edesmetta%2C%20also%20concluded%20that%20none%20of%20the%20eight%20people%20killed%20were%20Maoists%20and%20that%20the%20security%20forces%20may%20have%20opened%20fire%20on%20the%20unarmed%20crowd%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20judicial%20inquiry%20reports%20being%20submitted%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule%2C%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20to%20provide%20justice%20to%20the%20Adivasis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatia%20referred%20to%20recent%20incidents%20in%20which%20villagers%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20the%20fray%20of%20counter-insurgency%20measures%20against%20left-wing%20extremism%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20three%20crucial%20ways%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20governments%20have%20been%20similar%3A%20in%20terms%20of%20economic%20policies%2C%20counter-insurgency%20measures%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20respect%20for%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20justice%20and%20grievance%20redressal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20villagers%20in%20Sukma%E2%80%99s%20Tadmetla%20protested%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20men%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-villagers-protest-death-of-2-in-tadmetla-say-they-weren-t-maoists-101694446947398.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20police%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20October%2C%20two%20youngsters%20from%20Abujhmad%20village%20were%20also%20killed%20allegedly%20in%20an%20encounter.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20had%20accompanied%20their%20mothers%20to%20the%20ration%20shop%2C%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20walk%20away%20in%20Koelibeda%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20carry%20the%20load%20of%20grain%20home.%20They%20were%20taken%20away%20in%20front%20of%20their%20mothers.%20The%20mothers%20heard%20the%20shots%20and%20also%20saw%20the%20dead%20bodies%20when%20they%20were%20carried%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlmost%20every%20other%20day%20we%20keep%20hearing%20of%20activists%20and%20participants%20of%20peaceful%20protests%20being%20picked%20up%20and%20some%20of%20them%20incarcerated%20under%20false%20charges.%20This%20was%20the%20case%20before%20and%20after%20the%20change%20of%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Adivasis%20need%20control%20over%20their%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20for%20this%2C%20PESA%20and%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20need%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%20The%20way%20the%20government%20is%20going%20ahead%20with%20privatisation%20without%20adhering%20to%20these%20laws%20and%20opening%20security%20camps%20in%20many%20places%2C%20it%20is%20apparent%20that%20they%20are%20protecting%20mining%20companies%20and%20not%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetam%20said%20that%20the%20true%20test%20for%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20being%20from%20the%20tribal%20community%20himself%20will%20be%20how%20he%20handles%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20understand%20is%20that%20there%20is%20not%20much%20difference%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20on%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen.%20%3C%2Fem%3EBut%20how%20much%20will%20he%20(Sai)%20be%20able%20to%20resist%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20make%20pro-tribal%20policies%2C%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20test%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20because%20they%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D%20have%20governments%20both%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20in%20the%20state%20now.%20Earlier%2C%20they%20could%20deflect%20blame%20to%20each%20other%2C%20despite%20both%20being%20pro-capitalist%20in%20their%20policies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Adivasis%20reach%20positions%20of%20power%2C%20it%20is%20welcome%2C%20but%20the%20real%20test%20is%20whether%20their%20coming%20to%20power%20makes%20a%20difference%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20Adivasis%2C%20and%20if%20they%20will%20prove%20themselves%20to%20be%20better%20than%20their%20predecessors%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhatia%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704200457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10192940%2FGA6N65IaQAAU8Yf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhasdeo-arand-deforestation-raises-questions-of-adivasi-justice-for-chhattisgarhs-first-tribal-cm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20section%20of%20activists%20fighting%20for%20Adivasi%20rights%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20having%20a%20tribal%20chief%20minister%20if%20he%20continues%20to%20overlook%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20priorities%20to%20facilitate%20corporate%20interests%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhasdeo-arand-deforestation-raises-questions-of-adivasi-justice-for-chhattisgarhs-first-tribal-cm%22%2C%22cdnA