0air%20but%20might%20be%20seen%20as%20too%20serious%2C%20too%20trite%2C%20too%20silly%2C%20too%20political%2C%20too%20unpopular%20and%20thus%2C%20often%20ignored.%20Every%20episode%20asks%20a%20question%20floating%20around%20in%20the%20zeitgeist%20and%20looks%20at%20it%20from%20all%20the%20different%20angles.%20Guests%20join%20us%20to%20spark%20up%20the%20debate%20and%20add%20more%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire.%20We%20dabble%20in%20the%20personal%2C%20political%2C%20cultural%20and%20intellectual%20but%20always%20with%20a%20dash%20of%20humour%20and%20more%20than%20just%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20two%20disgruntled%20women%20who%20really%20enjoy%20extra%20salty%20and%20killjoy%20takes%20on%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghosh%20and%20Shringarpure%20say%20about%20why%20they%20started%20this%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvKo95RbkqIM%3Fsi%3DJvNIK_tI7-y8yzeE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Extra%20Salty%20has%20covered%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20that%20were%20on%20the%20hosts%E2%80%99%20minds%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo3Gv_mdgtnY%3Fsi%3DtrufHvrI8R9i4spI%5C%22%3Ewhy%20the%20Barbie%20doll%20is%20so%20popular%20in%20South%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtYj3iccasqk%3Fsi%3Dxi6UlSUCSFmXYajV%5C%22%3Ewhether%20Bollywood%20has%20a%20political%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvsuSBZGHtcg%3Fsi%3D-0P19GV3j6_eAUdo%5C%22%3Ewhether%20(and%20how)%20women%20can%20travel%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMMVzrfJFfa8%3Fsi%3Da5niFzhyAOeB6Kaq%5C%22%3Ewhat%20Palestine%20means%20for%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0KI3zD_nJ_Q%3Fsi%3DBddaZ_i_zR9n2sfl%5C%22%3Ewhat%20happens%20when%20caste%20representation%20enters%20popular%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20each%20episode%2C%20an%20expert%20guest%20has%20come%20in%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts%20and%20broaden%20the%20debate.%20And%20from%20lyricist%20and%20poet%20Hussain%20Haidry%20or%20author%20to%20rights%20activist%20Suchitra%20Vijayan%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20all%20had%20thought-provoking%2C%20detailed%20and%20often%20funny%20answers%20to%20some%20off-the-cuff%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20lots%20of%20great%20moments%20in%20these%20free-wheeling%20conversations%2C%20but%20the%20hosts%20summarise%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20liked%20best%20so%20far%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20part%20about%20these%20podcasts%20is%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20already%20been%20having%20these%20kinds%20of%20passionate%20conversations%20as%20good%20friends.%20But%20then%20a%20guest%20gets%20to%20join%20the%20party%20which%20forces%20us%20to%20focus%20and%20really%20delve%20into%20these%20burning%20questions.%20What%20we%20find%20exciting%20is%20that%20we%20start%20out%20with%20fairly%20adamant%20takes%20on%20the%20question%20but%20are%20often%20surprised%20or%20even%20converted%20to%20the%20opposite%20point%20of%20view%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20episode.%20And%20our%20truly%20favourite%20part%20is%20the%20stories%20that%20spontaneously%20unfold%20between%20us%20hosts%20as%20well%20as%20the%20guests.%20It%20was%20unexpected%20to%20hear%20Suchitra%20Vijayan%20speak%20about%20the%20hospitality%20and%20warmth%20that%20she%20experienced%20in%20conflict%20ones%20while%20travelling%20alone%20as%20a%20woman%20or%20to%20understand%20why%20Hussain%20Haidry%20graduated%20from%20a%20top%20MBA%20programme%20but%20ended%20up%20choosing%20an%20uncertain%20career%20as%20poet%20and%20Bollywood%20lyricist%20and%20we%20loved%20Bina%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%20the%20little%20boy%20who%20defied%20