%3E%20and%20instead%20focusing%20on%20revision.%20%E2%80%9CPast%20year%20papers%20are%20a%20great%20help%20to%20go%20over%20concepts.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20talent%20needs%20hard%20work%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20that%20he%20has%20a%20natural%20ability%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20competitive%20exams%2C%20Kalpit%20says%20talent%20on%20its%20own%20won%E2%80%99t%20take%20you%20very%20far.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20have%20special%20abilities%20to%20understand%20things%20a%20bit%20faster.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20use%20of%20talent%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrust%20your%20instincts%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20the%20results%20came%20out%20is%20etched%20in%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20memory.%20But%20he%20shares%20an%20anecdote%20of%20a%20time%20much%20before%20the%20D-Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20checking%20around%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20coaching%20classes%20that%20had%20released%20their%20answer%20keys.%20There%20was%20this%20one%20question%20in%20particular%20that%20was%20tricky.%20Everyone%20was%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327615%2Fengineer-animates-ncert-syllabus-turns-govt-schools-into-digital-classrooms-muskaan-dreams%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20had%20attempted%20it%20by%20an%20incorrect%20method.%20But%20I%20was%20sure%20I%20was%20right.%20I%20remember%20my%20friends%20saying%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98No%20one%20will%20think%20of%20such%20a%20strange%20way%20of%20solving%20this%E2%80%99.%20When%20the%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20my%20method%20was%20the%20right%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTrust%20your%20gut%20fee